## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential bias inherent in advocacy-focused publications. The analysis primarily reflects perspectives from organizations that support abortion rights, which may not encompass the full spectrum of views on the topic. Additionally, the data is current up to October 2023, and subsequent developments in legislation or public opinion are not reflected.